goto manage jeninks>plugins>jobDSL install it.

create a new item>seed_project>freestyle project >git >build>process job DSLs>job-dsl/nodejs.groovy


https://github.com/ammarqq/jenkins-course.git

not approved to use to resolve it goto jenkins>configure jenkins >in-process script approval>approve.

you will find nodejs example  as a project 

goto jenkins console

find / -name 'npm'

export PATH=$PATH:/var/lib/jenkins/tools/jenkins.plugins.nodejs.tools.NodeJSInstallation/nodejs/bin


cd /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/NodeJS...

npm start

> myapp@0.0.1 start /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/NodeJS example
> node index.js

Example app listening at http://:::3000

