Jenkins job DSL with docker build and publish

https://jenkinsci.github.io/job-dsl-plugin/

search dockerBuildAndPublish

referback to seed project>configure and add the 2ndfile in  the path of the file nodejsdocker.groovy


we need to add dockerhub credential
goto credential>on global>add credential>username:ammarqqqq>password:mypassword>ID:dockerhub

now build the seed project again.
